snippet.title: Paperquarium - Alpha gameplay
snippet.description:
Download now: https://deinol.itch.io/paperquarium

Video is missing a couple features like fish breeding (Two fish will be able to breed once they reach the adult state. Fishling will be colored as a mix of the parent's color.
